name: ChoccySwap
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: ChoccySwap is the first decentralized exchange on Chromia. Based on Uniswap V2, ChoccySwap lets you exchange any FT3 asset on the Chromia blockchain. You can vote on our governance platform using the CCY token.
